{"tid":926944,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南韓成年人  逾四分之一嚮往當公務員","createTime":"2018-12-03T22:23:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-04T05:45:08.000Z","uid":62257,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"10b06893a2172eaa109600f700936d479f8d47ea","tid":926944,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T22:23:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://money.udn.com/money/story/5602/3511933\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmoney.udn.com%2Fmoney%2Fstory%2F5602%2F3511933&d=rSuNKG3kIeh9F4kELdDWWp7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=150d184a\" target=\"_blank\">https://money.udn.com/money/story/5602/3511933</a><br />\n就業媒合平台Saramin HR調查1,143名成年人的工作偏好，發現高達26.7%的受訪者最嚮往進入公家機關，當中95%表示是因為當公務員較穩定。逾40%受訪者求職會優先考量工作穩定性。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/amphtml/南韓民調-擇偶職業-公務員最受青睞-070253378.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2Famphtml%2F%E5%8D%97%E9%9F%93%E6%B0%91%E8%AA%BF-%E6%93%87%E5%81%B6%E8%81%B7%E6%A5%AD-%E5%85%AC%E5%8B%99%E5%93%A1%E6%9C%80%E5%8F%97%E9%9D%92%E7%9D%9E-070253378.html&d=rSuNKG3kIeh9F4kELdDWWp7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=fa92053b\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/amphtml/南韓民調-擇偶職業-公務員最受青睞-070253378.html</a><br />\n2017年12月29日 上午7:02 [GMT]<br />\n<br />\n（中央社記者姜遠珍首爾29日專電）南韓婚姻媒介公司今天公開一份調查結果顯示，最受單身男女青睞的伴侶職業是公務員和事業單位人員。<br />\n南韓聯合新聞通訊社指出，這項調查上個月針對南韓全國25至39歲的1000名未婚男女，進行「2017年理想擇偶標準」問卷調查，獲得前述結果。<br />\n調查結果顯示，多數未婚男女希望另一半的職業為公務員或事業單位職員。<br />\n<br />\n未婚女性心目中理想丈夫年薪4900萬韓元（約合新台幣147萬元）、有2.73億韓元財產、任職公務員或事業單位、大學畢業、身高約177公分、比自己年長3-4歲。<br />\n未婚男性則希望未來的妻子年收入4200萬韓元、有1.82億韓元財產、任職公務員或事業單位、大學畢業、身高約164公分、比自己小3-4歲。<br />\n選擇配偶考慮的選項，35.7%的男性和35.1%的女性回答「性格」最重要。另外男性看重女性的外貌（18.2%）和價值觀（7.6%）；而女性重視男性的經濟能力（17.3%）和家庭環境（9.5%）。<br />\n男性計劃結婚的平均年齡為34.9歲，女性為33.7歲。男性認為一定要結婚的受訪者比重為37.6%，高於女性25.1%。整體來看，收入和學歷越高，認為一定要結婚的人越多。1061229"},{"pid":"e7cf5aae2f5d6ca7e5ba86d6c874effd5a781e77","tid":926944,"uid":51343,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T22:24:33.000Z","msg":"香港成年人 逾四分三嚮往當公務員<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fefa894505faabd17f8cfd6642d7f75b437c44d","tid":926944,"uid":37733,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"e7cf5aae2f5d6ca7e5ba86d6c874effd5a781e77","tid":926944,"uid":51343,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T22:24:33.000Z","msg":"香港成年人 逾四分三嚮往當公務員<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T22:32:57.000Z","msg":"呢個真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b8df9f278e494d541f0915e53db98198736cc90","tid":926944,"uid":140769,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T22:34:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5782ffb05e325401fa1979f2089cb634928071d9","tid":926944,"uid":183090,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6b8df9f278e494d541f0915e53db98198736cc90","tid":926944,"uid":140769,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T22:34:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T23:13:52.000Z","msg":"唔悶？<br />\n日日都係做個啲野其實同返普通工差唔多"},{"pid":"bf8cf1adef19eca9a8aae84abf55cee22160edc0","tid":926944,"uid":87600,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e7cf5aae2f5d6ca7e5ba86d6c874effd5a781e77","tid":926944,"uid":51343,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T22:24:33.000Z","msg":"香港成年人 逾四分三嚮往當公務員<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T23:18:43.000Z","msg":"係十成十都嚮往<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c46d9e65ec0c965b489e6bb4fba79c08fe67db76","tid":926944,"uid":70042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T23:29:25.000Z","msg":"要成200萬資產<br />\n食泡菜都咁貴"},{"pid":"8f802b9d4ecceea4e14faea001623be9ca559c67","tid":926944,"uid":170365,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"